dct_description_sm: Depths shown contours and gradient tints. Shows maritime boundaries, maritime claim lines, 12- and 200-nautical-mile line/arc, drawn area shown on Chinese maps, shipping lines. "This map is for illustrative purposes only. The limits shown are drawn according to the best available information as of 1 December 1995. They are not necessarily recognized by the United States or by the countries shown." "737328 (R01788) 12-95."
